Design:

Design Patterns:
 x Characters - decorator pattern
 
 x Monsters - factory pattern
 
 x Movement - controller pattern
 
 x User, dungeon status - state pattern
 
 Make 10 - 20 dungeon steps/options
 
1. Use 4 design patterns contained within the design patterns book. (50%)

2. Program a fully working application in Java to highlight the design patterns you learned (no compile/not running is an automatic fail)

3. Implement some unit tests. Doesn't have to be complete coverage, minimum test 2 design patterns (25%)

4. write up reflecting the challenges and difficulties you faced and how you learned from them(25%)